<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fires appear to kill individuals in the Santa Monica Mountains (Keeler-Wolf and Evens 2006). Seeds from unburned refugia establish new stands. This alliance is adapted to dry, semi-desert coastal cliffs and bluffs where fires are naturally rare. It is not considered a fire-type alliance.</div>
